item.title: CVE-2023-34999|2024-09-25T15:35:46.960Z -- rts -- vlink%20virtual%20matrix%20software
item.description: A command injection vulnerability exists in RTS VLink Virtual Matrix Software Versions v5 (< 5.7.6) and v6 (< 6.5.0) that allows an attacker to perform arbitrary code execution via the admin web interface.
